    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/logo.PNG?t=1732633112\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >浸入赛博朋克时代的亚人少女生活</h2><br><br>《Erophone·Re》是一款互动式解密ADV。通过偶然捡到的神秘手机Erophone，你将得以窥见隐于平静都市中的亚人社会，遇见个性鲜明的亚人少女们。在逐渐了解她们身世的同时，或许你还会发现这个世界更深的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/15e485012493934b8abe8444aba12b39.avif?t=1732633112\" width=600 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/1ae31392360e6b4dca988aa6f315f203.avif?t=1732633112\" width=600 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/9732a5778fb10698f24c6f1eca5450dc.avif?t=1732633112\" width=600 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/a77f0ec2499723ebcac138e098fe8340.avif?t=1732633112\" width=600 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/7b42b766a125e86c88deffda2dffc74e.avif?t=1732633112\" width=600 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >隐藏着无数可能性的日常</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/12269f61d39b1133f6be9b13980d6514.avif?t=1732633112\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>富足却堕落的城市，诺鲁玛。<br>无趣的日常琐事中，时而隐藏着亚人的蛛丝马迹。<br>暗中活跃的亚人管理局与财团，也在阴影中伸出了爪牙。<br>在一触即发的矛盾间，突然流传于都市传说中的神秘代码，又意味着什么？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开她们与Erophone隐藏的秘密</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/aside.PNG?t=1732633112\" /></span><br><br>亚人们隐藏的秘密，在Erophone下无所遁形。<br>对一些亚人来说，被亲密的人识破伪装并非坏事，反倒恰好是卸下重担的契机。<br>只是对太多人而言，即便真相就在眼前，却也容易视而不见。<br>而这台能揭晓一切秘密的Erophone，又有着怎样的过去？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><br>复古的Galgame玩法。追溯黄金时代的美好，没有无谓的重复操作。每次点击都将给予新反馈。<br>全动态人物演出。最大程度展示美少女的魅力。<br>不局限于选项的动态交互解谜玩法。你的行动至关重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832740/extras/bd33fa4ab59f6f7be567cb2263ba33ef.avif?t=1732633112\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
